This repository contains my coursework and solutions for the **42 Singapore** curriculum. I am using this journey to master the "black box" of computer science‚Äîunderstanding how memory, compilation, and algorithms work at the hardware abstraction layer. In many ways, this is my "leap into the unknown," moving from data insights to the foundational logic that powers them.

